Resource Profile: Cumulative Radiation Dose (Fixed)

Official URL: https://mitre.org/fhir/space-health/StructureDefinition/cumulative-radiation-dose Version: 0.5.3
Active as of 2025-12-29 Computable Name: CumulativeRadiationDose
